<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Navigation Bar</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/assign3.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <b href="#home">Home</b>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="box" id="home">
            <h1>Welcome To My Website</h1>
            <p>This is a simple webpage with a navigation bar and content sections.</p>
            <p>I made this page using basic HTML and CSS.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="box" id="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>
                We are learning web development. This website is created for practice.
                It contains a navbar, heading, paragraph, images, list, and contact form.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="box" id="services">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Web Page Design</li>
                <li>HTML Practice</li>
                <li>CSS Styling</li>
                <li>Basic Website Layout</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Training Schedule</h2>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Day</th>
                    <th>Topic</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Day 1</td>
                    <td>Portfolio Page</td>
                    <td>Completed</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Day 2</td>
                    <td>Registration Form</td>
                    <td>Completed</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Day 3</td>
                    <td>Navigation Bar</td>
                    <td>Running</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="box" id="gallery">
            <h2>Gallery</h2>
            <img src="images/img1.png" alt="Gallery 1">
            <img src="images/img2.png" alt="Gallery 2">
            <img src="images/img3.png" alt="Gallery 3">
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Important Notice</h2>
            <p>Practice HTML tags daily and complete all assignments on time.</p>
            <p>Use simple code first, then improve the design step by step.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="box" id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label><br>
                <input id="name" type="text" placeholder="Enter your name"><br>

                <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
                <input id="email" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email"><br>

                <label for="message">Message:</label><br>
                <textarea id="message" rows="4" placeholder="Enter your message"></textarea><br>

                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 My Simple Website</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
